# Orekhov, Republic of Adygea

}}
Orekhov () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Dukmasovskoye Rural Settlement of Shovgenovsky District, the Republic of Adygea, Russia. The population was 133 as of 2018. There are three streets.
Geography
Orekhov is located  west of Khakurinokhabl (the district's administrative centre) by road. Mokronazarov is the nearest rural locality.
